# Copy to `.env` if your shell loads dotenv tools. Prefer exporting in your shell for one-off commands.
#
# --- LLM Wiki Manager (see schema/wiki-manager.md) ---
#
# Neutral parent template checkout (fork diff upstream / lineage reference).
# Conceptually the git parent of domain children; in practice many neutral tooling
# changes are proven in a child (e.g. Shaolin) first, then cherry-picked here.
# WIKI_MANAGER_COMPARE_ROOT=/absolute/path/to/LLM Wiki Base Model
#
# Registered children (paths must match schema/wiki_family_registry.v1.json rows).
# WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_SHAOLIN=/absolute/path/to/Shaolin Monastery Research System
# WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_TAI_PAN=/absolute/path/to/Tai-Pan Wiki
#
# Adding another sibling: extend managed_children[] in schema/wiki_family_registry.v1.json
# (unique id / label / path_env), expose path_env here, then run `make coord-list`.
# Example extra row keys only — create your own PATH_ENV_NAME and uncomment when real:
# WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_EXAMPLE=/absolute/path/to/Example Domain Wiki
#
# Typical smoke on a workstation with repo checkouts beside each other:
#   export WIKI_MANAGER_COMPARE_ROOT="/abs/LLM Wiki Base Model"
#   export WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_SHAOLIN="/abs/Shaolin Monastery Research System"
#   make coord-status-json
#
# Fork-delta (script diffs vs children) is not run from this repo. Use the LLM Wiki
# Base Model checkout: `make fork-delta`, optional `CHILD_PATH_OVERRIDES=…` for
# platform/scripts-style children (see that repo's schema/fork-sync.md and README).
